SKIN-FRIENDLY : Mush hooded towels are composed of bamboo fiber, which is naturally hypoallergenic and free of any additives that could affect the sensitive skin of kids. As a result, our hooded baby towel is a safe, natural, and first choice for kids.  
, SUPER ABSORBENT : The Bamboo Fabric is more absorbent & breathable than any other fabric due to a wider cross section. This allows it to absorb 4x times more water while preventing dampen odor common in other cotton towels.  
, SOFTER THAN SOFT : The bamboo fabric is super-soft and gentle on the skin. The towel is made from bamboo which provides a silky soft touch while absorbing all traces of moisture efficiently from the body's surface. The soft plush fabric ensures comfort, longevity, and absorbency.  
, KIDS ESSENTIAL : When you’re checking off Kids’ essentials, “Mush baby hooded towel,” is at the top of the list. Whether it’s for a boy or girl, or you’re looking for a unisex gift, helps make life a little easier for your fellow parents.  
, QUALITY : unique designs, made up with soft and skin friendly fabric. Hooded towels are value-priced.

COMFORTABLE : When babies are swaddled, they sleep better & feel safe as babies are used to being wrapped tightly in the womb. Bamboo Fabric is weightless & thermo-regulating which helps to regulate the body temperature based on the weather.  
, SOFTER THAN SOFT : The bamboo fabric is super-soft and gentle on your baby’s skin. The soft plush fabric wraps around your baby for a comfortable sleep. It is also the best choice for rash prevention.  
, MULTIPURPOSE : Mush Bamboo Swaddles can be used as a play mat, a blanket, a burp cloth, a nursing cover, a picnic blanket. It is one of the best baby shower gifts for every new mom.
